Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:02.53,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}プレパラート越しに見える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.77,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}ひび割れた　空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:14.47,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}廃墟の屋上に　たどり着くは綿毛の
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:20.46,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}ささやきを囲む　僕らは歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:28.11,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}灰色の地上に　飾られた光の
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.05,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}轟をまとう　僕らは花束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:41.81,JP_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\xshad2\yshad4}むしられた翼を　
